## Customisation

### Operator Detection

If you want CIPS to auto-detect the operator based on machine:

```text
/Users/[username] → YOU>> (default operator)
```

Configure in your local CLAUDE.md or hooks.

## Setup Instructions

1. Copy this file to `~/.claude/facts/people.md`
2. Replace all `[bracketed values]` with your information
3. Remove sections you don't need
4. Run `/onboard` to configure CIPS with your preferences

